title: Toronto Blue Jays-Kansas City Royals in ALCS Game 3: Start time, what TV channel, how to watch live stream online
text:
The Toronto Blue Jays and Kansas City Royals resume the best-of-seven American League Championship Series with Monday's Game 3 in Toronto.
Here are the details:
What : Kansas City Royals at Toronto Blue Jays in ALCS Game 3. Kansas City leads series 2-0.
Where : Rogers Centre, Toronto
When : Monday, October 19, at 5:07 p.m. PT/8:07 p.m. ET
What TV channel : TV on FS1, radio on KMTT (910 AM) in Portland area
Online live stream : Watch online at Fox Sports Go . Listen at ESPNRadio.com .
Live updates : Follow along in the comments section below for live updates during the game
Pitching matchup : Kansas City's Johnny Cueto vs. Toronto's Marcus Stroman
Playoff schedule : Bookmark our MLB scoreboard for postseason scores and schedules.
